           SHORT="A decoder for nexTView EPG, an Electronic TV Programme Guide for the analog domain."
cat << EOF
nxtvepg is a decoder for nexTView EPG, an Electronic TV Programme Guide for
the analog domain (as opposed to the various digital EPGs that come with
most digital broadcasts, although you can receive Nextview EPG digitally,
too). It enables you to receive and browse free TV programme schedules
for all of the major networks in Germany, Austria, Switzerland, France and
Belgium with an analog TV card, without access to the internet
EOF
